description:
Have you ever asked, “Who is God?" 

Undoubtedly, we can all agree that God is a mystery. However, the beautiful thing is that God reveals Himself to those willing to see through the eyes of faith.

God reveals Himself through nature and through the Scriptures. But, what about the Godhead and the fact that there are THREE distinct persons in the Godhead? 

Listen to Pastor Ted Wilson’s message as he answers the question, “Who is God?” and gives a clear explanation of the Godhead. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e3wQKwOGFlo&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo_ANrUJhHN2_4bSlMDTjuqQ&index=97
